{"tid":2514941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢排台灣啲警察做乜嘢出曬事","createTime":"2021-05-03T14:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T14:48:24.000Z","uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d265bfe967e9f0897f47cae6f4d59db86302248a","tid":2514941,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"先係將唔配合盤查嘅民眾壓落地，然後最近台北市警察局一個派出所被古惑仔掃場，結果所長自己delete閉路電視片，再安排警察同古惑仔開記者會握手言和。呢排台灣啲警察做乜嘢出曬事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"medium\">日前發生在桃園中壢後車站教音樂女教師詹慧玲，<strong><span class=\"red\">遇員警無緣無故盤查而拒絕，被以柔道大外割壓制在地，並強制帶回派出所</span></strong>，上手銬釘腳鐐，備受傷害和侮辱，最後送地檢署簡單訊問才開釋，前後已折騰九小時方恢復自由<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.peoplenews.tw/news/cd863c4b-2369-4736-90c5-09afa3aa7032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.peoplenews.tw%2Fnews%2Fcd863c4b-2369-4736-90c5-09afa3aa7032&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=fca24b02\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.peoplenews.tw/news/cd863c4b-2369-4736-90c5-09afa3aa7032</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span class=\"medium\">承認滅證！台北市松山分局中崙派出所上個月（4月）16日發生黑衣人闖入，10名四海幫黑衣人為追罵松山分局體技教官楊忠蒞，<strong><span class=\"red\">竟衝進派出所砸毀警用電腦，事後派出所長竟將監視器畫面刪除涉嫌滅證</span></strong>，引發社會譁然。今天（2日）下午北市警局長陳嘉昌出面說明，公布還原的96秒監視器關鍵影像畫面，也調出所長與巡佐「合議」刪除監視器的畫面，確認是所長在黑衣人闖入當天晚上便自行將監視器格式化。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210502/AWDF6LCIZ5BLJE6J2BFWZVOKGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210502%2FAWDF6LCIZ5BLJE6J2BFWZVOKGY%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOOaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=8002f239\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210502%2FAWDF6LCIZ5BLJE6J2BFWZVOKGY%2F&h=3ec82bea\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20210502/AWDF6LCIZ5BLJE6J2BFWZVOKGY/</a></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d2f2a0ce6cf9484a881cab6ddee376d35bccc052","tid":2514941,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:47:06.000Z","msg":"有咩事當然入蔡婆數🚬"},{"pid":"6c4a2e0501d39f0abdcc88e31af4e0e5d72517b9","tid":2514941,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"黑警就一定有<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bc4af90e9d9820333b1855f748fb349c226185","tid":2514941,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:48:24.000Z","msg":"台灣警察呢啲叫專業判斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又想帶風向"}]}